{"tid":1122661,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"【佔中九子判刑如下，今晚荔枝角收押所聲援】時間：4/24（今晚）7時正  地點：荔枝角收押所門外","createTime":"2019-04-24T05:11:21.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-24T20:34:00.000Z","uid":25558,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"078b71ceb3638b2104ac3b4d83c44acf3214b59f","tid":1122661,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-24T05:11:21.000Z","msg":"【佔中九子判刑如下，今晚荔枝角收押所聲援】時間：4/24（今晚）7時正  地點：荔枝角收押所門外<br />\n<br />\n社會民主連線<br />\n35 分鐘 &middot; <br />\n<br />\n【佔中九子判刑如下，今晚荔枝角收押所聲援】<br />\n<br />\n．戴耀廷 16月監禁<br />\n．陳健民 16月監禁<br />\n．朱耀明 16月監禁、緩刑2年<br />\n．陳淑莊 押後宣判<br />\n．邵家臻 8月監禁<br />\n．張秀賢 200小時社會服務令<br />\n．鍾耀華 8月監禁、緩刑2年<br />\n．黃浩銘 8月監禁<br />\n．李永達 8月監禁、緩刑2年  <br />\n<br />\n傘運義工發起今晚到荔枝角收押所舉行燭光集會撐「九子」詳情如下：<br />\n <br />\n時間：4/24（今晚）7時正<br />\n 地點：荔枝角收押所門外<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://scontent-hkg3-2.xx.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/57788192_10156056977610785_1823052972490227712_n.png?_nc_cat=109&amp;_nc_ht=scontent-hkg3-2.xx&amp;oh=23b3b239335fe2d8125592bcc3d33090&amp;oe=5D75CB27\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent-hkg3-2.xx.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2F57788192_10156056977610785_1823052972490227712_n.png%3F_nc_cat%3D109%26_nc_ht%3Dscontent-hkg3-2.xx%26oh%3D23b3b239335fe2d8125592bcc3d33090%26oe%3D5D75CB27&h=56bf40c6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/hklsd/photos/a.101378395784/10156056977595785/?type=3&amp;theater\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fhklsd%2Fphotos%2Fa.101378395784%2F10156056977595785%2F%3Ftype%3D3%26theater&d=zdm3SfM4sEUVnXmiquxubLM5QgR%2FpIHXQ%2BfAgFWVWJ0%3D&h=641ac5bd\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/hklsd/photos/a.101378395784/10156056977595785/?type=3&amp;theater</a><br />\n<br />\n地址<br />\n九龍蝴蝶谷道 3/5 號<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n如何前往<br />\n<br />\n乘坐港鐵荃灣線（荔枝角站 C 出口）。<br />\n乘坐港鐵東涌線（在荔景站轉荃灣 線至荔枝角站 C 出口）。<br />\n乘坐港鐵機場快線（在青衣站轉東涌線，再在荔景站轉荃灣線至荔枝角站 C 出口）。<br />\n乘坐西鐵（在美孚站轉港鐵荃灣 線至荔枝角站 C 出口）。<br />\n乘坐城巴 E21 號（由香港國際機場（赤鱲角機場）開出）。<br />\n乘坐隧道巴士 102 號（由筲箕灣開出）<br />\n（長荔街巴士站下車）﹔<br />\n乘坐隧道巴士 904 號（由堅尼地城開出）<br />\n（長荔街巴士站下車）﹔<br />\n乘坐隧道巴士 905 號（由灣仔碼頭開出）<br />\n（長荔街巴士站下車）﹔<br />\n乘坐九巴 6 號（由尖沙咀開出）<br />\n（長荔街巴士站下車）﹔<br />\n乘坐九巴 2A 或 6D 號（由牛頭角開出）<br />\n（長荔街巴士站下車）﹔<br />\n乘坐九巴 68X 號（由元朗開出）<br />\n（長荔街巴士站下車）﹔<br />\n乘坐九巴 60X 號（由屯門市中心開出）<br />\n（長荔街巴士站下車）﹔<br />\n乘坐九巴 86 號（由黃坭頭開出）<br />\n（長荔街巴士站下車）﹔<br />\n乘坐九巴 86A 號（由沙田圍開出）。<br />\n（長荔街巴士站下車）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.csd.gov.hk/images/image/facility/facility_ind/ins_lckrc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.csd.gov.hk%2Fimages%2Fimage%2Ffacility%2Ffacility_ind%2Fins_lckrc.jpg&h=2434b76f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\ngoogle map<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.google.com.hk/maps/place/Lai+Chi+Kok+Reception+Centre,+Lai+Chi+Kok+Correctional+Institution,+Butterfly+Valley+Rd,+Lai+Chi+Kok/@22.337017,114.1460988,15z/data=!4m2!3m1!1s0x340407557c5ec545:0x36eee5232c1372b5\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.google.com.hk%2Fmaps%2Fplace%2FLai%2BChi%2BKok%2BReception%2BCentre%2C%2BLai%2BChi%2BKok%2BCorrectional%2BInstitution%2C%2BButterfly%2BValley%2BRd%2C%2BLai%2BChi%2BKok%2F%4022.337017%2C114.1460988%2C15z%2Fdata%3D%214m2%213m1%211s0x340407557c5ec545%3A0x36eee5232c1372b5&d=zdm3SfM4sEUVnXmiquxubLM5QgR%2FpIHXQ%2BfAgFWVWJ0%3D&h=e870253c\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.google.com.hk/maps/place/Lai+Chi+Kok+Reception+Centre,+Lai+Chi+Kok+Correctional+Institution,+Butterfly+Valley+Rd,+Lai+Chi+Kok/@22.337017,114.1460988,15z/data=!4m2!3m1!1s0x340407557c5ec545:0x36eee5232c1372b5</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/bYo6WRM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbYo6WRM.jpg&h=99ff931e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"63f025d2797269b7d603ef0dd6164c5d3c308162","tid":1122661,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-24T06:51:58.000Z","msg":"荔枝角地鐵站行去大概五分鐘<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/fPuRo6L.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FfPuRo6L.jpg&h=b7e5e430&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b0edd93a64c1f32ab0d80f1fe64d74fe71c69e28","tid":1122661,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-24T08:56:56.000Z","msg":"1900"},{"pid":"47090d81681e40dbb12e7952d2d1495d164c0108","tid":1122661,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-24T09:29:35.000Z","msg":"荔枝角站C出口<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ByX30xF.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FByX30xF.jpg&h=8f8dd898&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"9398a9e7a3d0f0e7a4c47437be362c437635f1bf","tid":1122661,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-24T10:41:29.000Z","msg":"到咗， 好多記者同天線發射器， 差佬都唔少。"},{"pid":"34cc61703d51cce85bfcf58e049acb4ac6435a53","tid":1122661,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-24T11:03:37.000Z","msg":"見到洪朝豐坐喺第二排"},{"pid":"d6852a218b387456d94bc4fea4421371dcbbad8b","tid":1122661,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-24T11:08:37.000Z","msg":"好迫爆呀"},{"pid":"16a302a582377025011d63ccdc0ded11fffdbf88","tid":1122661,"uid":14941,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-24T13:20:55.000Z","msg":"現場為左歡迎戴耀延<br />\n一班人齊心拍叫「佔領中環！正式啓動」<br />\n好正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7f2114974a1536462b7877004c92b46c94b188a1","tid":1122661,"uid":220721,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-24T15:27:09.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"18e181f1eb332dfb355651d1628cc049fb241116","tid":1122661,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7f2114974a1536462b7877004c92b46c94b188a1","tid":1122661,"uid":220721,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"16a302a582377025011d63ccdc0ded11fffdbf88","tid":1122661,"uid":14941,"lik